body_html:
GPU compilation on windows does take a long time, due to Visual Studio not properly parallelizing the compilation when using an external compiler (nvcc).
Looks like you already have a solution to the reported issue. We would be happy to review and accept your solution to the repository. Would you like to create a Pull Request?
